<p>The <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">reflect.DeepEqual</code> is &gt;72 times slower than our generated comparator. <a href="https://github.com/vitessio/vitess/blob/master/go/vt/sqlparser/ast_equals.go">Check out the code</a></p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>We also need to be able to do a deep-clone of the AST. While exploring different alternative plans, we clone parts of the AST, so we can change it without changing the original. <a href="https://github.com/vitessio/vitess/blob/master/go/vt/sqlparser/ast_clone.go">Check out the code</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
